Harrowing scenes in Soweto this morning as 14 people have been shot and killed at a tavern in Orlando. eNCA reporter Nqobile Madlala is on the scene.#DStv403   JOHANNESBURG - Harrowing scenes in Soweto after 15 people were shot and killed at a tavern in Orlando. Gauteng Police Commissioner Elias Mawela said masked men entered the liquor outlet in Nomzamo park in Orlando East. WATCH: Witness says masked men attacked Soweto tavern They opened fire on patrons using high-calibre weapons. "We were called in the early hours of the morning, around 12.30am. When we arrived on the scene, 12 people were confirmed dead," he said. Mawela said 11 others were taken to hospital. Two remain in a critical condition. Harrowing scenes in Soweto this morning as 14 people have been shot and killed at a tavern in Orlando. #DStv403